    in the battle area.\n[Start of Your Turn] If your opponent has a Digimon, \uFF1CDelay\uFF1E
    \n\u30FB Return 1 red Digimon card from your trash to the top of the deck. Then,
    if you don't have a Digimon, you may play 1 red Digimon card with 2000 DP or
    less from your trash without paying the cost."
